snippet.title: Digimon Tamers: Brave Tamer Translation (Dev Note #1)
snippet.description: First video showing off the in-progress translation patch for Digimon Tamers: Brave Tamer on the Wonderswan! This is very unpolished at the moment, but I wanted to show some current in-game footage as a preview. Thanks to LazerMutt4 for the new English logo!
